title: https://github.com/Microsoft/windows-dev-box-setup-scripts
a
https://github.com/Microsoft/windows-dev-box-setup-scripts
: choco scripts for automating setting up a dev machine (installs git, Visual Studio, Visual Studio Code etc.)

inline_content.Text: : choco scripts for automating setting up a dev machine (installs git, Visual Studio, Visual Studio Code etc.)

title:
choco install -y golang
choco install -y git
choco install -y 7zip
choco install -y conemu
choco install -y cmake
choco install -y nodejs
choco install -y python2
choco install -y llvm
choco install -y windbg -params '"/SymbolPath:c:\symbols"'

choco install -y visualstudio2017community 
choco install -y visualstudio2017-workload-manageddesktop 
choco install -y visualstudio2017-workload-netcoretools 
choco install -y visualstudio2017-workload-universal
choco install -y visualstudio2017-workload-nativedesktop --package-parameters "--add Microsoft.VisualStudio.ComponentGroup.NativeDesktop.Win81 --add Microsoft.VisualStudio.ComponentGroup.NativeDesktop.WinXP"

choco install -y visualstudio2017-workload-nativedesktop --package-parameters "--includeOptional"
or components: Microsoft.VisualStudio.Component.Windows81SDK
or: Microsoft.VisualStudio.ComponentGroup.NativeDesktop.Win81, Microsoft.VisualStudio.ComponentGroup.NativeDesktop.WinXP

choco install -y potplayer
choco install -y calibre
choco install -y sharex

Upgrading Visual Studio
choco upgrade -y visualstudio2017community visualstudio2017-workload-manageddesktop visualstudio2017-workload-netcoretools visualstudio2017-workload-universal
choco upgrade -y visualstudio2017-workload-nativedesktop --package-parameters "--add Microsoft.VisualStudio.ComponentGroup.NativeDesktop.Win81 --add Microsoft.VisualStudio.ComponentGroup.NativeDesktop.WinXP"
